uction improves the sharpness of vessel contours • In body CTA a dose reduction of {\textgreater}50{\%} might be possible when using raw data-based iterative reconstructions, while image quality can be maintained.},
author = {Winklehner, Anna and Karlo, Christoph and Puippe, Gilbert and Schmidt, Bernhard and Flohr, Thomas and Goetti, Robert and Pfammatter, Thomas and Frauenfelder, Thomas and Alkadhi, Hatem},
